        </item>
        <item>
            <title>iPhone 16 發布會邀請函証實造假　製作者自爆是用 AI 生成圖片的惡作劇</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/iphone16-apple-event-invite-is-fake/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone16-apple-event-invite-is-fake</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/iphone16-apple-event-invite-is-fake/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 05:08:03 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中熱話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交網絡]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1257773</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">知名 Apple 爆料用戶 <a href="https://x.com/MajinBuOfficial">@MajinBuOfficial</a> 早前在 X 平台上分享他收到了疑似是 Apple iPhone 16 發布會的邀請函，從邀請函中得知活動將於太平洋時間 9 月 10 日上午 10 時（即香港時間 9 月 11 日凌晨 1 時）舉行。最新消息為邀請函已經被証實造假，單純是一場對爆料用戶的惡作劇。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">According to what I was told by a source who asked to remain anonymous, the new Apple event where the iPhone 16 will be presented, will be held on September 10 2024. <br />This should be the cover of the invitation <a href="https://t.co/7jGoafHaOU">pic.twitter.com/7jGoafHaOU</a></p><p>&mdash; Majin Bu (@MajinBuOfficial) <a href="https://twitter.com/MajinBuOfficial/status/1825466723023139243?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">August 19, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Fun fact: i made the &quot;leaked&quot; Apple Event invite in less than 10 minutes using figma and an Ai generated texture   <br />and i sent it to the leaker just because i was bored <a href="https://t.co/3tX9QgUy4p">pic.twitter.com/3tX9QgUy4p</a></p><p>&mdash; Lore (@lorevfx) <a href="https://twitter.com/lorevfx/status/1825815959166189789?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">August 20, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">X 用戶 <a href="https://x.com/lorevfx">@lorevfx</a> 將自己製作這個假的 iPhone 16 發布會邀請函的整個過程上傳，並表示自己使用免費的線上設計工具 Figma 和 AI 工具輔助，僅花了不足 10 分鐘便完成整個偽造的邀請函。至於製作這個惡作劇的原因，他表示單純是出於無聊。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="zxx" dir="ltr"><a href="https://t.co/DYuPXLyuDc">pic.twitter.com/DYuPXLyuDc</a></p><p>&mdash; Lore (@lorevfx) <a href="https://twitter.com/lorevfx/status/1825915465677324521?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">August 20, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>Lore 將當初與 Majin Bu 的聊天記錄上傳，並表示自己用一個愚蠢的故事就成功説服了 Majin Bu 將這個假的邀請函發布。邀請函被証實造假之後，Majin Bu 並沒有因為被欺騙而感到生氣，反而十分欣賞他的付出甚至將偽造的邀請函製成了桌布。網民直指 Lore 是天才，不過都有網民認為現時的爆料用戶不負責任，完全不理會資料的真確性就將其發布。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.cultofmac.com/news/iphone-16-event-invite-leaks-september-2024?fbclid=IwY2xjawEzlcJleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHV1eGIQhpOGJhbGZfeDUqy6K5bH419byCRInqTSABpCwS9-Yn9mvnK_F8A_aem_YAltz9zXqwfxJck0YwIR6w">Cult of Mac</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/21/iphone-16-pro-assembled-india-first-time/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 16 Pro 印度製造，傳富士康已著手訓練員工</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/20/iphone-16-invitation-letter/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple iPhone 16 發布會邀請函流出　日期時間 + 或有新顏色</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/20/iphone-16-pro-color-desert-titanium/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 16 Pro 相機零件曝光，引證全新沙漠鈦金屬色機身選擇</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/iphone16-apple-event-invite-is-fake/mobile-phone/">iPhone 16 發布會邀請函証實造假　製作者自爆是用 AI 生成圖片的惡作劇</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
