        <item>
            <title>【評測】模壽 x BLITZWAY 真三一萬能俠　LED 燈效驚艷 + 跳齒式關節</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/moshowtoysblitzwaygetter/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=moshowtoysblitzwaygetter</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/moshowtoysblitzwaygetter/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 04:30:48 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1256633</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近年來，真三一萬能俠合金 Figure 大家都見得多了，多廠也相繼有推出各自有獨特風格的版本，而今次最新推出的是由模壽與 BLITZWAY 合作，真三一萬能俠合金 Figure，售價為人民幣$980，摺合約港幣$1,100 左右，確實引起了不少關注，而這個版本又有什麼特點呢？小編已收到送測版本，立即為大家開箱。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0644-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0644-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0644-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">當然又是大大盒的了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257713" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0643-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0643-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0643-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">極具份量，整箱重 5.2KG。</p><p>外觀設計方面，這款真三一萬能俠相當忠於原作。最為人矚目的是其標誌性的「水桶腰」造型，線條簡潔有力。表面採用高光澤度處理，尤其是紅色部分，呈現出類似跑車烤漆的質感，視覺效果十分搶眼。然而，這種處理也帶來了一些小問題，如容易留下指紋，需要經常擦拭保養。頭部設計亦相當出色，不僅還原了真三一萬能俠鋭利的眼神，還提供了多種可替換的表情部件，雖然效果不是特別明顯，但也體現了製作團隊的用心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0303-694x510.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="510" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0303-694x510.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0303-scaled.jpg 1226w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257715" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0356-694x407.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="407" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0356-694x407.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0356-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="_DSC0318" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938406694/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938406694_2d58069163_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0318" width="1024" height="688" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0327" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938323858/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938323858_304de9c8e8_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0327" width="1024" height="601" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0319" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938073516/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938073516_04cfd7b039_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0319" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0322-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0322-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0322-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257718" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0323-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0323-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0323-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0325-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0325-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0325-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0313-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0313-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0313-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257723" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0314-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0314-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0314-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>燈光效果是這部真三一萬能俠的一大特色。頭部、胸口、腰部和手臂等多個部位都配備了 LED 燈組，可説是全身都可亮齊燈光效果，電池方面就要用到 AG1 及 AG13 電池，每種需要 8 粒。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257724" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0307-694x455.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="455" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0307-694x455.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0307-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257725" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0310-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0310-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0310-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257726" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0311-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0311-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0311-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>由於今次是測試版，尚有地方會再作改良，例如手腕裝 LED 位置的扣位，會有扣不穩的情況掉下，廠方説到時真正出貨時這方面會作出改良；現時的卡扣設是想可以讓用家容易點換電，但又要卡得到可負擔到重型武器兩把大斧的重量。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257739" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0309-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0309-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0309-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="_DSC0412" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938323688/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938323688_86b1f82b9b_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0412" width="1024" height="624" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>其中，胸口和腿部的燈光效果表現優秀，亮度充足，光線分佈均勻。然而，頭部和手臂的燈光效果則稍顯遜色。真三一還附帶了一些特效配件，如可發光的烈陽閃光彈，增加了擺 pose 的趣味性。</p><p><a title="_DSC0334" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938528675/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938528675_432f6ac23d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0334" width="1024" height="642" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257727" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0340-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0340-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0340-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257728" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0347-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0347-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0347-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257729" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0348-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0348-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0348-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257730" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0349-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0349-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0349-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257731" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0350-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0350-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0350-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257732" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0351-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0351-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0351-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>可動性方面，這部真三一表現達到中上程度。雖然某些部位的活動範圍有限，但整體來説足以應對大多數常見 Pose。值得一讚的是，真三一萬能俠大量採用了齒輪結構，大大提升了關節的穩定性，帶來了極佳的把玩手感，小編就特別喜愛這種跳齒式關節了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0324-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0324-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0324-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257721" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0328-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0328-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0328-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>配件方面，真三一配備了多種配件，包括標誌性的真三一戰斧和真三一鐮刀。這些武器尺寸誇張，造型霸氣，能夠有效增強真三一的視覺衝擊力。另一個值得一提的配件是重達 2 公斤的展示地台，地台採用了動畫中 Invader 的造型，增加了展示效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257734" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0352-694x337.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="337" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0352-694x337.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0352-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257735" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0354-694x358.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="358" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0354-694x358.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0354-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257736" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0355-694x360.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="360" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0355-694x360.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0355-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257737" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0420-694x486.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="486" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0420-694x486.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0420-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257738" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0421-694x429.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="429" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0421-694x429.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0421-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>Action Pose</h2><p><a title="_DSC0386 (1)" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938073351/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938073351_898b539fa0_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0386 (1)" width="1024" height="623" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC0361" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938323738/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938323738_fa764d4e3d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0361" width="966" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0408" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938406619/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938406619_a65da83f4f_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0408" width="848" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0372" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53937169757/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53937169757_1e86d35c68_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0372" width="1024" height="650" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>這款模壽與 BLITZWAY 合作的真三一萬能俠是一個有潛力的作品，它在造型設計、部分燈光效果和穩定性等方面表現出色，為真三一萬能俠愛好者提供了一個不錯的選擇。而大約 HK$1,1xx 的定價，可説是高性價比了。不過，如果能夠簡化地台以降低價格，可能更能提升吸引力。</p><p><a title="_DSC0340" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100